def removedDigit(n, s, k): count =0 for i in range(1,n+1): temp = list(filter(lambda x: int(x) in s, str(i))) if(count+temp.__len__() >= k and temp.__len__()!=0): return temp[k-count-1] else: count+=temp.__len__() return -1
